name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
High schoolization of universities
On November 5, a student from Xiamen Institute of Technology jumped off a building.
It is reported that Xiamen Institute of Technology has recently formulated a strict high school-like management system, requiring students to carry school bags, prohibiting them from playing online games, and even prohibiting them from having bicycles in their studies
At the same time, because the principal loves running, he arbitrarily stipulates that all students in the school need to run. Students in their first and second years need to run 400 kilometers to get credits, and students in their third and fourth years need to run 200 kilometers to graduate.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On November 6, it was reported online that several students of the Department of Breast Surgery of Sun Yat-sen Memorial Hospital of Sun Yat-sen University (the Second Affiliated Hospital of Sun Yat-sen University) suffered from rare breast cancer. On November 7, a staff member of the Party Committee Office of the Second Affiliated Hospital of Sun Yat-sen University responded, "The relevant online information is false information. We are investigating and handling it. There will be official announcements on the follow-up."
